text: Siret is a surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Luis Siret (1860–1934), a Belgian-Spanish archaeologist and illustrator * Nicolas Siret (1663–1754), a French composer and organist * Adolphe Siret (1818--1888), Belgian historian, biographer, essayist, poet and writer * (1745--1798), French grammarian and philologist
